Good men.

555
00:43:16,191 --> 00:43:21,151
为了那个小子而牺牲掉他们，值得么？
Are you ready to sacrifice their lives for that kid?

556
00:43:22,197 --> 00:43:24,131
弗兰克
Hey, Frank.

557
00:43:24,432 --> 00:43:26,297
- 弗兰克 - 嗯？
- Frank. - Yeah?

558
00:43:26,468 --> 00:43:29,801
我没有想要牺牲任何人的生命
This is not about me ruining anybody's life.

559
00:43:29,971 --> 00:43:32,235
懂么？而是因为你
Okay? This is about you.

560
00:43:33,375 --> 00:43:35,070
听到我说什么吗？
You hear me?

561
00:43:36,077 --> 00:43:37,669
嗯
Yeah.

562
00:43:39,014 --> 00:43:40,675
你看过那个小子纪录了么？
You look at that kid's jacket?

563
00:43:42,217 --> 00:43:43,844
我看过
I did.

564
00:43:44,052 --> 00:43:47,419
- 持械抢劫，侵犯他人，殴打老年妇女... - 我从来没有持械抢劫过！
- Armed robbery, assault, beats old women... - I never had no armed robbery!

565
00:43:47,589 --> 00:43:50,717
为了抢去社保金，他殴打一位老年妇女
Beats old women over the heads, steals their Social Security checks.

566
00:43:50,892 --> 00:43:53,884
- 只有一次，我曾经... - 闭嘴
- One time, I used... - Shut up. Shut up.

567
00:43:54,062 --> 00:43:55,927
噢，不，不要叫他闭嘴
Oh, no, don't tell him to shut up.

568
00:43:56,097 --> 00:44:01,296
不，杰克，让他讲 那个小子，他很聪明
No, Jack, listen to him. No, that kid, he's sharp.

569
00:44:01,469 --> 00:44:02,731
其实他在耍你
Yeah, he's playing you.

570
00:44:04,806 --> 00:44:07,001
他比你聪明
He's sharper than you are.

571
00:44:07,742 --> 00:44:09,835
他在唬弄你，知道吗？
He's telling you stories, right?

572
00:44:10,512 --> 00:44:12,844
他肯定对你说他要做一个好公民
He wants to be a good citizen.

573
00:44:14,182 --> 00:44:15,410
要上教堂
Go to church.

574
00:44:16,017 --> 00:44:18,042
要为她母亲买房子
Buy his mother a house.

575
00:44:18,219 --> 00:44:22,087
但实际上他一生大部分的时间都在监狱里
But he has spent more than half his life in prison.

576
00:44:24,125 --> 00:44:29,358
两个小时前 他还因为非法持械被捕
Two hours ago, he was sitting in a cell for weapons possession.

577
00:44:29,531 --> 00:44:32,329
- 他不会改变了 - 我没有...
- He's always gonna do what he has done. - I wasrt...

