- You all right? - Yeah. Frank's got him on the other side.

580
00:44:41,976 --> 00:44:43,273
我的枪也被他抢了
He's got my gun too.

581
00:44:43,678 --> 00:44:45,737
如果到现在，你都还执迷不悟的话...
Now, if you can't see how wrong this is...

582
00:44:45,914 --> 00:44:48,906
我只能这样说
...I promise you I will speak from my heart...

583
00:44:49,951 --> 00:44:52,419
我会在你的葬礼上为你念悼词
...when I give the eulogy at your funeral.

584
00:44:53,588 --> 00:44:55,283
所以
So...

585
00:44:56,524 --> 00:44:58,219
你相信那小子？
...do you believe the kid?

586
00:45:01,029 --> 00:45:03,429
还是相信你的前拍档？
Or do you believe your ex-partner?

587
00:45:08,336 --> 00:45:10,896
弗兰克，我们就在门的另一边
Frank, we're right on the other side of the door.

588
00:45:11,072 --> 00:45:12,835
因为...
Because...

589
00:45:14,209 --> 00:45:16,336
如果你相信他的话...
...if you believe the kid...

590
00:45:18,947 --> 00:45:21,177
