- You heard him, right, Jack? - Not now, Eddie.

617
00:48:05,613 --> 00:48:08,776
- 小声点 - 他说他从不开门
- Keep your voice down. - He said he never opens the door.

618
00:48:08,950 --> 00:48:11,441
你知道这意味着什么，对吗？
You know what that mean, right?

619
00:48:13,988 --> 00:48:15,979
