01:00:51,792 --> 01:00:54,124
数数有多少人
Count how many people are here.

795
01:00:55,062 --> 01:00:58,054
大家把手举起来，谢谢
Everybody put your hands up, please.

796
01:00:58,666 --> 01:01:02,659
我们纽约警局，我们在执行公务 请大家回到人行道上去
N. Y.P.D., we got a situation here. We need you people back on the sidewalk.

797
01:01:02,836 --> 01:01:06,738
- 不要越过路障 - 26，28个，好的，谢谢
- Stay behind the barricade. - Twenty-six, 28. Okay, thank you.

798
01:01:06,907 --> 01:01:09,535
这就是所有的人了？ 请不要哭，不要哭
That's everybody? Please, don't cry, don't cry.

799
01:01:09,710 --> 01:01:14,977
没事的，不要惊慌 冷静点，好么？谢谢
Everything's gonna be all right, just relax. Stay calm, okay? Thank you.

800
01:01:15,149 --> 01:01:17,208
- 多少？ - 31
- What is it? - Thirty-one. Thirty-one.

801
01:01:18,719 --> 01:01:24,555
好吧，这里大概有40人
Okay, we have about 40 people on the bus.

802
01:01:24,959 --> 01:01:27,086
好的
Okay, that's good.

803
01:01:27,461 --> 01:01:30,396
杰克，我对你直说好了
You know, it's important that we're clear with each other, Jack.

804
01:01:30,831 --> 01:01:33,925
特警队和人质谈判小组都在这里
ESU and HNT are in place.

805
01:01:36,170 --> 01:01:39,606
整个街区都被封锁了，杰克
The block is sealed, Jack. It's a frozen zone.

806
01:01:39,907 --> 01:01:44,640
我们好好处理这件事情， 这样大家都好下台
So let's work this out so everybody can go home, all right?

807
01:01:44,812 --> 01:01:48,475
这样对大家都好
That's all we wanna do. Just end it, nice and easy.

808
01:01:49,650 --> 01:01:51,117
杰克？
Jack?

809
01:01:51,285 --> 01:01:54,152
杰克？你还想怎么样，老兄？
Jack? This is as far as you go, buddy.

810
01:01:54,488 --> 01:01:55,477
说话啊...
Keep talk...

811
01:02:14,341 --> 01:02:17,242
- 大家还好吧？ - 嗯
- Is everybody okay? - Yeah.

812
01:02:17,945 --> 01:02:20,038
- 你好，你怎么样了？ - 很好
- Hi, how are you? - Good.

813
01:02:20,214 --> 01:02:22,079
你呢？
How are you?

814
01:02:22,249 --> 01:02:27,448
我们名字叫爱迪 大家都还好？
My name's Eddie. Hi, how you doing? Everybody's okay?

815
01:02:31,525 --> 01:02:32,992
你叫什么名字？
What's your name?

816
01:02:33,360 --> 01:02:35,828
- 克里斯蒂纳 - 克里斯蒂纳
- Christina. - Christina.

817
01:02:36,096 --> 01:02:40,863
那是个很漂亮的名字 你多大了？
That's a pretty name. How old are you, Christina?

818
01:02:42,603 --> 01:02:44,969
- 七岁 - 七岁了
- Seven. - Seven years old.

819
01:02:47,675 --> 01:02:50,644
我要给你做个草莓蛋糕 我知道怎么做，让我找找
And my strawberry recipe... I know I got one. Let me see.

820
01:02:51,512 --> 01:02:54,379
我的草莓蛋糕呢？让我看看
Where's my strawberry recipe? Let's see.

821
01:02:55,149 --> 01:02:58,676
这是怎么做天使蛋糕
Angel-food-cake recipe right here.

822
01:02:59,753 --> 01:03:03,154
找到了，草莓蛋糕！
Here we go, strawberry fan.

823
01:03:03,891 --> 01:03:05,984
看这个蛋糕的样子
See right here on the top?

824
01:03:06,293 --> 01:03:08,124
我可以把它做成扇子的样子
I can put a fan on the top.

825
01:03:08,796 --> 01:03:12,664
就是一个中国扇子的样子
You know, like a Chinese fan?

826
01:03:13,033 --> 01:03:15,160
我可以把蛋糕做成那样
I could do that.

827
01:03:16,203 --> 01:03:17,966
你什么时候生日？
Whers your birthday?

828
01:03:18,405 --> 01:03:22,205
- 9月22日 - 哦，那很快了嘛
- September 22nd. - Oh, so that's soon.

829
01:03:22,376 --> 01:03:27,143
就快8岁了，对吧？ 那是个很好的日子
Gonna be 8 years old, huh? That's gonna be a good day for you.

830
01:03:27,481 --> 01:03:29,005
你的生日呢？
Whers your birthday?

831
01:03:30,551 --> 01:03:32,815
今天，实际上
Today, actually.

832
01:03:33,187 --> 01:03:36,588
- 是啊 - 祝你生日快乐
- Yeah. - Happy birthday to you.

833
01:03:40,928 --> 01:03:44,386
是啊，每天都有人过生日
And, yeah, every day is somebody's birthday, you know.

834
01:03:44,565 --> 01:03:47,728
我将来糕点店的标语就会是这个：
That's gonna be the motto for my shop:

835
01:03:47,901 --> 01:03:49,960
“每一天都是一个生日”
"Every day's a birthday," you know.

836
01:03:50,137 --> 01:03:54,073
没想到在我的生日会发生这样的事情，可是...
I didn't know my birthday was gonna turn out like this, but...

837
01:03:54,241 --> 01:03:59,042
至少我还活着，我已经很高兴了
Yeah, I'm glad to be, you know, here, alive, you know.

838
01:04:01,448 --> 01:04:03,348
- 说吧，杰克 - 希恩
- Right here, Jack. - Yeah, Sheehan.

839
01:04:03,817 --> 01:04:05,182
局长
Commissioner, sir.

840
01:04:05,352 --> 01:04:07,149
- 希恩? - 说吧
- Sheehan? - Right here.

841
01:04:07,321 --> 01:04:09,846
好吧，这是我的条件
All right. This is what I want.

842
01:04:10,023 --> 01:04:13,254
我要你帮我接通副检察官马克当娜
I want you to get me Assistant District Attorney MacDonald...

843
01:04:13,427 --> 01:04:17,227
还有一位法庭书记员，和一位记者
...a court stenographer and somebody from TV.

844
01:04:17,398 --> 01:04:19,195
我认识的记者
Somebody that I would recognize.

845
01:04:19,366 --> 01:04:22,028
我要他们到车上来 帮我录一段证词
I want them to come on the bus and record sworn testimony.

846
01:04:22,202 --> 01:04:26,434
这完了后，我会让每个人安全地离开
When I get what I want, I'll let everybody out. Safely.

847
01:04:26,607 --> 01:04:31,442
- 我需要一些时间 - 别跟我来这一套
- That's a tall order. It'll take some time... - Just do it. I'm not in the mood, okay?

848
01:04:31,612 --> 01:04:33,910
15分钟之类让他们到这里来
Get these people here in 15 minutes...

849
01:04:34,081 --> 01:04:36,606
否则我会开始向乘客开枪
...or I'm gonna shoot these passengers one at a time...

850
01:04:36,784 --> 01:04:39,252
- 然后把他们的尸体扔到车外 - 杰克，冷静点
...and throw them out the door. - Jack, be cool, okay?

851
01:04:39,420 --> 01:04:42,389
别冲动，这件事情可以和平解决
Let's not do anything rash. This thing can end without bloodshed.

852
01:04:42,556 --> 01:04:44,524
- 一切好商量，好么？ - 15分钟
- Okay? We can work this... - Fifteen minutes.

853
01:04:44,691 --> 01:04:47,387
杰克？杰克？
Jack? Jack?

854
01:04:50,564 --> 01:04:52,361
他挂了
He's gone.

855
01:04:54,234 --> 01:04:55,826
好吧，大家都站起来
All right, everybody on your feet.

856
01:04:57,304 --> 01:05:00,273
- 杰克，你干什么？ - 我得让这些人下去
- Jack, what are you doing? - Gotta get these people off this bus.

857
01:05:00,441 --> 01:05:03,706
你不是才打了电话么？ 你让检察官来，他们不是同意了么？
But you just made your call. You called the DA. They said they'd come.

858
01:05:03,877 --> 01:05:06,175
- 这些人都会来的 - 没人会来的，知道么？
- Everybody's coming. - Nobody's coming, okay?

859
01:05:06,346 --> 01:05:07,904
没人会来？为什么？
What do you mean, nobody's coming?

860
01:05:08,081 --> 01:05:11,312
5分钟内，他们会强行进攻这个巴士
They're gonna breach this bus in less than five minutes.

861
01:05:11,485 --> 01:05:14,613
- 他们会杀了我，杀了你 - 杰克，我还要作证呢？
- They're gonna kill me, kill you... - Jack, what about testifying?

862
01:05:14,788 --> 01:05:17,086
我们应该在这里等他们来 然后一切都会结束
We're right here. We can go. We can end this.

863
01:05:17,257 --> 01:05:19,691
- 我们等他们来，然后作证 - 不会有人作证
- We can testify. - Nobody's testifying.

864
01:05:20,694 --> 01:05:22,787
一切都完了，爱迪
It's all over, Eddie.

865
01:05:22,963 --> 01:05:25,158
我们输了
We lose, kid.

866
01:05:37,211 --> 01:05:39,941
- 雷 - 弗兰克.
- Hey, Ray. - Frank.

867
01:05:40,113 --> 01:05:41,705
你们...?
You...?

868
01:05:43,383 --> 01:05:44,680
你们要进攻了？
You guys going in?

869
01:05:44,852 --> 01:05:47,286
局长还没有下命令
The commissioner hasn't given us the green light yet.

870
01:05:47,454 --> 01:05:53,450
嗯，我要提醒你，他杀了两个警察
Well, I don't need to remind you that he shot two of us.

871
01:05:55,496 --> 01:05:57,430
我知道该怎么做了
Enough said.

872
01:05:57,898 --> 01:06:00,799
车上有40个平民 把他们救出来
We got maybe 40 civilians on that bus. Get them out.

873
01:06:00,968 --> 01:06:03,061
不能让任何人受伤， 包括我们自己的人
I don't want anybody hurt, including our guys.

874
01:06:03,237 --> 01:06:06,331
局长，没有人会受伤的 我们的突击队员都是训练有素的
Nobody's gonna get hurt, commissioner. These guys know what to do.

875
01:06:13,547 --> 01:06:16,072
- 有情况出现 - 大家注意了
- We have movement. - Let's move in.

876
01:06:16,250 --> 01:06:19,083
- 不要开枪，重复，不要开枪 - 朝汽车靠近，行动
- Hold your fire. Repeat, hold your fire. - Move in to the bus. Let's go.

877
01:06:22,089 --> 01:06:23,852
喂，怎么了？
Hey. What...?

878
01:06:25,826 --> 01:06:26,815
鲍勃.
Bob.

879
01:06:29,696 --> 01:06:30,890
你出去的时候
When you get outside...

880
01:06:31,064 --> 01:06:32,929
- 生日快乐 - 谢谢
- Happy birthday. - Thank you.

881
01:06:33,100 --> 01:06:35,762
他们会把你带到一个隔离区 那里会很混乱
They'll take you to a holding area. It'll be hectic.

882
01:06:35,936 --> 01:06:38,837
- 可是要是人人都出去了... - 听我说，你听我说
- But everybody's out there... - Listen to me, listen to me.

883
01:06:39,006 --> 01:06:41,566
你一旦离开了这个封锁区 你便可以逃走
Once you get outside that perimeter, you just get lost.

884
01:06:41,742 --> 01:06:44,734
- 可是如果他们？ - 不要停下，你一定不要停下
- What if they...? - Keep moving. You just keep moving.

885
01:06:44,912 --> 01:06:46,243
听我说，你看起来不错
Come here. You look great.

886
01:06:46,413 --> 01:06:48,176
喂，灰色西装哦
Hey, gray suit.

887
01:06:49,316 --> 01:06:50,840
这可是你要的灰色西装
Got you a gray suit.

888
01:06:51,018 --> 01:06:54,215
好了，大家把手举在头上，别回头
All right? Hands in the air, folks. Don't look back.

889
01:07:02,296 --> 01:07:05,231
手举在头上，都结束了，结束了
Hands in the air, you'll be all right. You'll be all right.

890
01:07:17,444 --> 01:07:18,968
下一位，对不起
Next. Sorry.

891
01:07:28,755 --> 01:07:30,620
快，快，跟我来
Come on, come on, let's go!

892
01:07:30,791 --> 01:07:32,622
- 他这是在做什么？ - 我怎么知道？
- What is he doing? - How should I know?

893
01:07:32,793 --> 01:07:34,886
- 我现在不知道 - 你居然用这种口气...
- I'll let you know when I know. - Don't you...

894
01:07:35,062 --> 01:07:37,428
我明白了自然会告诉你 滚开！
I'll let you know when I know. Out of my face!

895
01:07:47,608 --> 01:07:49,906
凯乐，过来帮帮我
Kaller, give me a hand with them!

896
01:07:54,047 --> 01:07:56,413
波比?这边，这边
Bobby? Right there. Right here.

897
01:07:56,950 --> 01:07:59,646
- 就是他 - 喂，你干嘛？
- That's him. That's him. - Hey, man!

898
01:08:00,754 --> 01:08:02,881
- 不是他 - 让他走吧
- It's not him. - Let him go.

899
01:08:03,056 --> 01:08:05,115
- 他穿了别人的衣服 - 什么？
- The dude, he changed. It's not me. - What?

900
01:08:05,292 --> 01:08:07,954
- 他换上了一套西装，灰色西装 - 灰色西装，好的
- He's in a suit, a gray suit. - Suit, gray suit.

901
01:08:28,882 --> 01:08:31,544
- 有31人下了车 - 那车上还有8个人
- We count 31. - That leaves eight people on the bus.

902
01:08:31,718 --> 01:08:33,379
不，我是最后一个人
No, I was the last one off the bus.

903
01:08:33,553 --> 01:08:36,454
车上就只剩下那个拿枪的人
The only person left on that bus is the guy with the gun.

904
01:08:37,524 --> 01:08:39,355
- 那你们行动吧 - 开始行动
- Then go, do it! - Let's go, let's go.

905
01:08:39,526 --> 01:08:42,757
行动开始
- Get your people out there. Let's go. - Come on, let's go.

906
01:08:43,563 --> 01:08:46,691
莫斯里还在车上 那个小子不在车上，我们搜查了...
Mosley is still on the bus. That kid is here somewhere. We checked...

907
01:08:46,867 --> 01:08:48,664
波比，别废话了
Bobby, I don't care what you checked.

908
01:08:48,835 --> 01:08:51,395
再给我搜一遍，马上 你们，去那边
Check it again, now. Go. You guys, that way.

909
01:09:05,218 --> 01:09:10,178
我是警探杰克 莫斯里，警号227
This is Detective Jack Mosley. Shield number 227.

910
01:09:21,201 --> 01:09:23,761
这可能会是我最后的遗嘱
I guess this will be my last will and testament.

911
01:10:17,591 --> 01:10:18,819
别开枪！
Don't shoot!

912
01:10:19,192 --> 01:10:20,591
别开枪！
Hold your fire!

913
01:10:20,761 --> 01:10:22,558
别开枪！别开枪！
Do not shoot! Do not shoot!

914
01:10:22,729 --> 01:10:24,924
- 那个人是谁？ - 别开枪！
- Who is that? - Hold your fire!

915
01:10:25,732 --> 01:10:27,791
- 别开枪！ - 那个人就是那个证人么？
- Hold your fire! - Is it that wit from the 32?

916
01:10:29,402 --> 01:10:31,666
给我查清楚那个人是谁
Get on your goddamn radio. Find out who that is.

917
01:10:31,838 --> 01:10:33,601
别开枪！
Guns down, hold your fire!

918
01:10:35,142 --> 01:10:36,370
别开枪！
Don't shoot!

919
01:10:36,543 --> 01:10:38,477
别开枪！
Don't shoot! Don't shoot!

920
01:10:40,580 --> 01:10:41,842
别开枪！
Don't shoot!

921
01:10:42,015 --> 01:10:43,778
别开枪！
Don't shoot!

922
01:10:47,254 --> 01:10:50,655
- 站住！不要靠近那部汽车！ - 别开枪！
- Do not move! Step away from the bus! - Don't shoot, hold your fire!

923
01:10:50,824 --> 01:10:52,815
- 别开枪！ - 离开公共汽车！
- Do not shoot! - Get away from the bus!

924
01:10:52,993 --> 01:10:54,119
别开枪
Hold your fire.

925
01:10:55,128 --> 01:10:58,996
杰克，是我
Jack. Jack, it's me. Jack Mosley!

926
01:10:59,633 --> 01:11:01,533
杰克，是我，爱迪
It's me, Eddie, Jack.

927
01:11:04,371 --> 01:11:05,770
查克.贝里
Chuck Berry.

928
01:11:06,106 --> 01:11:07,596
查克.贝里
Chuck Berry.

929
01:11:08,074 --> 01:11:11,601
查克.贝里， 他因为抢劫入狱
Chuck Berry, he got locked up for armed robbery.

930
01:11:11,778 --> 01:11:14,042
但是他后来改变了
He changed. He changed.

931
01:11:15,782 --> 01:11:19,309
巴里.怀特，他偷了300各轮胎
Barry White, he stole 300 tires.

932
01:11:19,486 --> 01:11:24,617
你能想象他偷了300个轮胎么？他后来也变了
Can you picture big Barry White stealing 300 tires? He changed.

933
01:11:24,791 --> 01:11:27,157
你说...你说人本性难移
You said... You said people don't change.

934
01:11:27,727 --> 01:11:30,127
- 但是实际上人会变的 - 爱迪
- People change. - Eddie.

935
01:11:30,864 --> 01:11:33,230
- 怎么了？ - 你把我害死了
- What? - You're killing me.

936
01:11:33,500 --> 01:11:37,231
第三组，行动 重复，第三组，行动
Team three, breach the bus. Repeat, team three, breach the bus.

937
01:11:37,404 --> 01:11:39,872
第三组靠近汽车
Entrance team moving in.

938
01:11:52,986 --> 01:11:55,477
让开！
Get out of the way!

939
01:11:56,323 --> 01:11:58,917
把头埋下！ 遮住耳朵和眼睛！
Head down! Cover your ears and your eyes!

940
01:12:04,497 --> 01:12:05,725
- 别开枪 - 跟进，跟进！
- Hold fire. - Go, go!

941
01:12:06,132 --> 01:12:08,191
- 跟进！ - 别开枪！
- Go, go, go! - Hold your fire!

942
01:12:08,368 --> 01:12:10,392
他到底要干嘛？
This is a nightmare.

943
01:12:26,286 --> 01:12:27,617
别开枪！
Hold fire!

944
01:12:59,152 --> 01:13:00,949
- 快点！行动！ - 当心！
- Let's go! Move, move, move! - Stay down!

945
01:13:01,121 --> 01:13:02,588
- 过来，过来！ - 这里
- Move up! Move up! - Come here.

946
01:13:02,756 --> 01:13:05,486
第二组，报告你们情况？
Team two, status?

947
01:13:05,659 --> 01:13:08,753
快！
Go ahead! Take it! Go!

948
01:13:39,359 --> 01:13:41,623
车上没有人
The bus is empty.

949
01:13:41,795 --> 01:13:43,490
他们从前门逃跑了！
They went through the bus doors!

950
01:13:43,663 --> 01:13:47,292
他们在这栋楼里！ 封锁这里！
They're in the goddamn building! Seal it off!

951
01:13:47,968 --> 01:13:50,835
- 汽车上没有人 - 他们跑进了楼里
- All clear. The bus is empty. - They've entered the building.

952
01:13:53,173 --> 01:13:54,765
封锁这栋楼，开始搜索
Seal the building, start a search.

953
01:13:54,941 --> 01:13:57,409
当心，他杀了两个警察，你们要小心
Remember, heads up. He just shot two cops. Be careful.

954
01:13:59,746 --> 01:14:01,646
杰克，我要告诉你一件事情
Jack, I gotta tell you something.

955
01:14:01,815 --> 01:14:04,215
喂，杰克，听我说
Hey, man. Jack, listen to me, man.

956
01:14:04,384 --> 01:14:06,443
