Jack, I wanna tell you something.

957
01:14:06,619 --> 01:14:10,316
等等，我告诉你件事情 这很重要
Hold on, hold on, wait. I gotta tell you something. It's important.

958
01:14:10,857 --> 01:14:13,325
振作点，我们走
Shit. Get up, go.

959
01:14:15,528 --> 01:14:17,428
妈的
Oh, shit.

960
01:14:18,598 --> 01:14:20,998
