Hey, sir. I'm a cop, all right? I'm on the job.

961
01:14:21,167 --> 01:14:23,192
我借你的电话用下
Look, I need that phone for a minute.

962
01:14:23,370 --> 01:14:24,962
看看你把我的西装弄成这样了
Look what you did to my suit, man.

963
01:14:25,505 --> 01:14:28,133
我就知道你会让我中弹的
I told you you was gonna get me shot.

964
01:14:29,142 --> 01:14:30,575
是我，我需要你的帮助
It's me. I need your help.

965
01:14:31,011 --> 01:14:35,107
一切都是因为我朋友毛里斯
All this started because my friend Maurice came by my house.

966
01:14:36,883 --> 01:14:40,341
两天前他到我家来
Two days ago, Maurice came by my house.

967
01:14:40,520 --> 01:14:41,919
