975
01:15:05,779 --> 01:15:08,009
那真是个凶兆
It's a very big sign.

976
01:15:08,181 --> 01:15:10,706
当心
Easy, easy, easy.

977
01:15:14,654 --> 01:15:19,023
你知道开个糕点店需要多少钱么？
You know how much it gonna take me to open the bakery?

978
01:15:21,428 --> 01:15:23,953
三万一千块钱
Thirty-one thousand dollars.

979
01:15:24,130 --> 01:15:28,863
