I went to Port Authority and I put the money in a locker.

981
01:15:37,644 --> 01:15:38,906
当我回家的时候
I get back to my house...

982
01:15:39,079 --> 01:15:41,411
我的缓刑辅导员在那里
...my parole officer's there...

983
01:15:41,581 --> 01:15:43,208
就在我家里
...in my house.

984
01:15:43,383 --> 01:15:46,216
他发现了毛里斯留下的枪
He got Maurice's gun in his hand.

985
01:15:46,386 --> 01:15:49,651
他看着我，很失望的样子
He looking at me like, "That's it, Eddie."

986
01:15:49,989 --> 01:15:51,889
他说这至少得判15年
And he's talking about 15 years, man.

987
01:15:52,459 --> 01:15:54,427
我吓呆了
I got so sick.

988
01:15:54,594 --> 01:15:58,155
后来检察官给我打来电话
Then the DA came to my cell...

989
01:15:59,632 --> 01:16:02,658
他给我看了那个警察的照片
...and he showed me the picture of that cop.

990
01:16:04,170 --> 01:16:06,001
然后就是你
Then I met you.

991
01:16:06,539 --> 01:16:11,442
杰克， 每天他们都要清理那些储物柜
Jack, they clean them lockers out every 24 hours.

992
01:16:12,879 --> 01:16:14,904
我的时间还挺紧的
I had a little schedule going, man.

993
01:16:16,282 --> 01:16:18,682
10点钟上法庭作证
Court at 10:00...

994
01:16:19,719 --> 01:16:21,983
12点赶到汽车站
...Port Authority at 12.

995
01:16:22,155 --> 01:16:24,146
喂，看着我，清醒点
Hey. Hey, look at me. Wake up.

996
01:16:24,991 --> 01:16:26,925
你不会在我面前死去，对么？
You ain't gonna die on me, are you?

997
01:16:29,095 --> 01:16:31,757
我怎么知道，我从来没有经历过死亡
I don't know, I never died before.

998
01:16:31,931 --> 01:16:34,229
你今天不会死的
It's not gonna happen today.

999
01:16:44,310 --> 01:16:45,800
