I gotta ask you one more favor.

1034
01:18:44,564 --> 01:18:47,089
很小的忙
Just a little favor.

1035
01:18:53,973 --> 01:18:56,271
喂，今天真的是你的生日？
Hey, is today really your birthday?

1036
01:18:56,442 --> 01:18:58,103
不是
No.

1037
01:18:58,278 --> 01:19:02,874
我说今天是我的生日 因为我不想小女孩那么害怕
No, I just said that because the little girl, she was so scared.

1038
01:19:03,583 --> 01:19:05,778
她很可爱
She was cute, man.

1039
01:19:06,686 --> 01:19:08,620
你生日是多久？
Whers your birthday?

1040
01:19:11,157 --> 01:19:13,990
- 我不知道 - 你不知道是什么意思？
- I don't know. - What do you mean, you don't know?

1041
01:19:15,962 --> 01:19:18,658
真的，我不知道
No, for real, I don't know.

1042
01:19:18,831 --> 01:19:22,767
我是在孤儿院长大的 那里太多的生日了
I'm not... I came up in foster care. Had a lot of birthdays.

1043
01:19:22,935 --> 01:19:27,770
但是你说有一个妹妹？你今天要去见的
But didn't you say...? You got a sister, right? That you're going to see?

1044
01:19:27,940 --> 01:19:30,932
是啊，我几个月前才发现
Yeah, I just found out about her a couple months ago.

1045
01:19:31,110 --> 01:19:33,169
- 你见过她么？ - 没有
- Never met your sister? - No.

1046
01:19:34,747 --> 01:19:37,580
那也是我去西雅图的原因，我想见她
That's why I'm going out to Seattle to meet her.

1047
01:19:38,685 --> 01:19:39,982
我很期待
I'm looking forward.

1048
01:19:40,153 --> 01:19:42,951
说不定她长得像安吉丽娜.朱丽呢
Maybe she turns out to look like Angelina Jolie.

1049
01:19:43,122 --> 01:19:46,387
我可不希望她只是我妹妹
Shit, if she do, I hope she ain't my sister.

1050
01:19:50,763 --> 01:19:53,061
你想要蛋糕上写什么字？
Hey, man, what you want on your cake, man?

1051
01:19:53,232 --> 01:19:55,393
我会给你做一个蛋糕的
You never told me. I gotta send you one, man.

1052
01:19:56,536 --> 01:19:59,403
- 我不需要什么蛋糕，爱迪. - 别这么不给面子，老兄
- I don't want no cake, Eddie. - Damn it, Jack, come on, man...

1053
01:19:59,572 --> 01:20:02,166
我想不起...
I can't think of anything that has happened in my life...

1054
01:20:02,342 --> 01:20:05,402
- 有什么我想写在蛋糕上面的 - 一句话都没有？
...that I would want written on a cake. - Nothing?

1055
01:20:07,547 --> 01:20:09,481
我不是一个好人，爱迪.
I'm not a good guy, Eddie.

1056
01:20:14,687 --> 01:20:16,814
我不是一个好人
I'm not a good guy.

1057
01:20:20,660 --> 01:20:22,491
好吧，那我也不是
Yeah, me neither.

1058
01:20:37,110 --> 01:20:38,338
- 戴安 - 弗兰克
- Diane. - Frank.

1059
01:20:38,511 --> 01:20:40,308
把钥匙给我
Give me the keys.

1060
01:20:40,480 --> 01:20:43,313
- 呆在车里别出来 - 这里可不是你的辖区，不是么？
- Stay in the car. - Little out of your sector, aren't you?

1061
01:20:43,483 --> 01:20:45,110
救命可不分什么辖区
Saving lives knows no bounds.

1062
01:20:45,284 --> 01:20:47,775
- 这你应该很清楚， 弗兰克. - 你看上去气色不错嘛
- You should know that, Frank. - You look good.

1063
01:20:47,954 --> 01:20:50,184
你看上去有点绝望 这可不像你
You look a little desperate. Doesrt suit you.

1064
01:20:50,356 --> 01:20:51,823
把门打开
Open the door.

1065
01:20:51,991 --> 01:20:54,221
快把门打开
Open the door. Open the door.

1066
01:20:55,661 --> 01:20:58,129
对不起，杰克，我就只能送你到这里了
Sorry, Jack, this is as close as I can get you.

1067
01:21:04,737 --> 01:21:06,864
好吧，算你走运
Like I said, you're looking good.

1068
01:21:11,544 --> 01:21:13,102
谢谢了，兄弟
Thanks, kid.

1069
01:21:14,213 --> 01:21:15,578
好吧，我们去法庭上
All right, come on, let's go.

1070
01:21:15,748 --> 01:21:18,216
不，等下
No, hey, hold on. Hold on a minute.

1071
01:21:18,384 --> 01:21:19,783
为什么？还等什么？
Why is that? Hold on for what?

1072
01:21:19,952 --> 01:21:21,852
你就到这里为止了
This is as far as you go too.

1073
01:21:22,021 --> 01:21:24,148
- 什么意思？ - 听我说，爱迪
- Come on, man. I don't... - Listen to me, Eddie.

1074
01:21:24,323 --> 01:21:26,757
- 怎么了？ - 听着
- What? - Listen.

1075
01:21:28,161 --> 01:21:30,857
你要去指证的这些人
Those guys you were gonna testify against...

1076
01:21:31,030 --> 01:21:33,089
- 这些警察 - 嗯？
...those cops? - Yeah?

1077
01:21:34,567 --> 01:21:35,966
我就是其中一个
I was one of them.

1078
01:21:44,444 --> 01:21:46,844
也就是说，你要去指证我
You were gonna testify against me too.

1079
01:21:49,482 --> 01:21:51,575
他们做的，我都做了
I did what they did.

1080
