我知道那很坏
We did some bad things.

1081
01:21:55,388 --> 01:21:58,585
我利用了你
I did another bad thing when I used you.

1082
01:21:59,826 --> 01:22:04,024
其实根本不需要你来指证我们
I was gonna let you do what I should have done.

1083
01:22:04,197 --> 01:22:07,223
我若干年前就应该自首了
What I should have had the courage to do six years ago.

1084
01:22:12,672 --> 01:22:14,037
对不起
I'm sorry.

1085
01:22:19,178 --> 01:22:23,410
你知道，要是今天不是你的话
You know, if you didn't come to get me today...

1086
01:22:24,450 --> 01:22:26,884
我现在已经死了
...l'd be dead right now.

1087
01:22:27,053 --> 01:22:28,850
