I was supposed to meet you.

1089
01:22:33,526 --> 01:22:35,756
是命中注定
That was the sign.

1090
01:22:36,162 --> 01:22:38,392
你救了我一命
You saved my life, kid.

1091
01:22:43,302 --> 01:22:45,827
保重了
Take care of yourself, kid.

1092
01:22:47,740 --> 01:22:48,968
