Thank you.

1093
01:22:49,509 --> 01:22:52,672
你可以做糕点了，爱迪师傅
Make cakes, Eddie the baker.

1094
01:23:00,386 --> 01:23:04,186
哦对了，你把车钥匙交给你的朋友
Oh, yeah. You give the car keys to your best friend.

1095
01:23:04,357 --> 01:23:07,053
你让他带老妇人去医院
You let him take the old lady to the hospital.

1096
01:23:07,226 --> 01:23:12,095
你在车站等那个梦中的女孩，对么？
You stay at the bus stop with the girl because she's the girl of your dreams, right?

1097
01:23:12,265 --> 01:23:14,665
所以一切都会好的
So everything's gonna be okay.

1098
01:23:15,568 --> 01:23:17,536
- 对吧？ - 嗯
- Right? - Yeah.

1099
01:23:18,804 --> 01:23:21,034
西雅图生活愉快！向你妹妹问好
Have fun in Seattle. Say hi to your sister.

1100
01:23:21,207 --> 01:23:22,799
好的
Yeah.

1101
01:23:27,046 --> 01:23:28,536
好吧
Yeah.

1102
01:23:29,849 --> 01:23:32,647
你载他去汽车站 保证他赶上那班车
Get him to the Port Authority. Make sure he gets on that bus.

1103
01:23:32,818 --> 01:23:34,046
- 卡尔，多谢了 - 不用
- Carl, thanks. - No problem.

1104
01:23:34,220 --> 01:23:35,619
好的
All right.

