Hell of a morning, huh?

1106
01:24:59,939 --> 01:25:01,201
那小子呢？
Where's the wit?

1107
01:25:03,542 --> 01:25:04,873
他不在了
You're looking at him.

1108
01:25:08,948 --> 01:25:10,813
我放他走了，弗兰克
I let the kid go, Frank.

1109
01:25:12,184 --> 01:25:16,143
- 你抓不住他了 - 去你的
- You're not gonna get to him now. - Bullshit.

1110
01:25:17,857 --> 01:25:19,119
