Then why?

1118
01:25:49,622 --> 01:25:51,647
你听我说，杰克，你和我...
Look, Jack, you and me...

1119
01:25:51,824 --> 01:25:56,818
我们一直就是这样做事的
...we did our business in a certain way.

1120
01:25:59,031 --> 01:26:02,558
即使是那些很棘手的案子， 我们也心照不宣
You never complained when we cleared the tough cases.

1121
01:26:02,735 --> 01:26:06,501
你以前什么都无所谓，直到...
It didn't bother you doing any of that until...

1122
01:26:07,873 --> 01:26:10,603
听我说，好么？听我说
Listen to me, all right? You listen.

1123
01:26:10,776 --> 01:26:13,677
